cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.DS, cs.RO

The paper proposes a deep reinforcement learning approach to improve the solution quality of the Travelling Salesman Problem. This involves learning a policy network to guide the selection of the next solution. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). The paper also involves optimization and search algorithms, which are relevant to cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.RO (Robotics).
